OL,6,FAssisted by a Russian interpreter,
OL,7,FMotin confirmed his identity before he
OL,8,Fpleaded not guilty to a single charge
OL,9,Fof the manslaughter of Filipino
OL,10,Fnational Mr Pernia on March 10.
OL,12,FJudge Lucraft set a further hearing on
OL,13,FSeptember 10 ahead of the defendant's
OL,14,Ftrial on January 12 2026.
OL,16,FMotin was charged over Mr Pernia's
OL,17,Fdeath after his vessel collided with
OL,18,Fthe American tanker Stena Immaculate
OL,19,Fnear the Humber Estuary on March 10.
