OL,6,FAll 23 people on the tanker were
OL,7,Frescued along with 13 crew from the
OL,8,FSolong, but Mr Pernia could not be
OL,9,Flocated.
OL,11,FMr Pernia was working in the forward
OL,12,Fdeck of the Solong, in an area where
OL,13,Fthere was an explosion.
OL,15,FThe collision happened at about 9.47am
OL,16,Fat 10.2 nautical miles from the
OL,17,Fnearest point on the coast, a previous
OL,19,Fhearing was told.
